Package: controlDim
Title: Dimensional Control Tools for Steel Panels
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person("Nataly", "Romaris", email = "nataly.romaris@udc.es", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Olamar", "Benavente", email = "o.benaventef@udc.es", role = "aut"),
      person("Ruben", "Fernandez-Casal", email = "rubenfcasal@gmail.com", role = "aut")
    )
Description: R package developed by the MODES group for the dimensional control of 
    steel panels in naval construction. It provides functions for 3D visualization, bounding 
    box calculations, panel border extraction, directional angle computation, disconnected 
    component detection, and other tools to support analysis and scientific publications.
